{"tid":204202,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救] R9 270新機boot唔起，用onboard apu開機認到","createTime":"2017-04-16T21:50:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-16T23:28:45.000Z","uid":25657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8656c16c3ea80916eba96c2bd1596533671877fd","tid":204202,"uid":25657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T21:50:51.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n<br />\n尋日砌咗部新機，除咗張display card全部都係新嘢<br />\n但係張舊卡R9 270就boot唔起，連bios畫面都見唔到，但其實佢可以入到Windows，只係見唔到嘢 （我用onboard個APU裝咗Windows）<br />\n用返APU boot起可以見到係GPU-Z見到部分資料，亦成功安裝Driver<br />\n<br />\n張卡係HIS R9 270 iPower IceQ X&sup2; Turbo Boost Clock 2GB GDDR5 <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hisdigital.com/un/product2-785.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hisdigital.com%2Fun%2Fproduct2-785.shtml&d=MUobR5x4uSQxHz8Khhk%2FvEbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=b615c27a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hisdigital.com/un/product2-785.shtml</a><br />\n<br />\nConfig:<br />\nZalman ZM600-GV<br />\nASRock B250M Pro4<br />\nIntel i5 7600k<br />\n8G DDR4<br />\n<br />\n大家覺得呢個情況係張卡壞定係唔compatible???<br />\n人在外地冇人可以幫手試到張卡係咪未壞，張卡放係度冇用三個月度，之前一直用開<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DY2a4Y2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDY2a4Y2.png&h=ef6099b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3gPdBOh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3gPdBOh.png&h=c8081e5c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c1227a195adc44d005db34d2b619959f99f4db22","tid":204202,"uid":38097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T21:52:35.000Z","msg":"原來intel出左apu"},{"pid":"b09b36b3e452c98709ad78bef9cc243ecedd4b25","tid":204202,"uid":25657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T21:57:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>原來intel出左apu</blockquote><br />\n唔識嘢，原來intel唔叫apu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab236dfcacc3839e04ca92331b85b29